{"tid":1294060,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府對示威者佔據旺角馬路表示遺憾　呼籲盡快散去","createTime":"2019-07-07T17:32:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T17:38:31.000Z","uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4eeeb418fa1094cd83c63ac1f2ea82588cbc21e7","tid":1294060,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T17:32:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1467112-20190708.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1467112-20190708.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Tc8prIKBo9hF1z3tnQ%2BJRtRt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=eccf240a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1467112-20190708.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=ebe7a2a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1467112-20190708.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"114fe21b15fa43239725d67d67bb89b666987347","tid":1294060,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T17:33:02.000Z","msg":"政府發言人表示，晚上有部分示威者佔據旺角一帶的馬路，導致交通阻塞、商業活動受到影響及對市民造成不便，並與警方對峙，對此表示遺憾，呼籲示威者盡快和平散去。<br />\n<br />\n發言人表示，昨日下午在尖沙咀的遊行，大體上以和平、理性的方式進行，特區政府相關部門和港鐵公司全程提供協助及維持秩序，盡量減低對使用西九龍高鐡站的市民及旅客的影響。<br />\n<br />\n另外，警方在社交網站發帖文，呼籲在旺角及油麻地一帶參與非法集結的示威者儘快離開，亦提醒與示威無關的市民為人身安全應該和平離開，切勿參與任何違法行為。"},{"pid":"2a176d65d4f1ad10a73cdb9ec9ce902b58a282a3","tid":1294060,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T17:34:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b875bbcdbd65947c5398877bc661a56e64a2e9ce","tid":1294060,"uid":36238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T17:35:13.000Z","msg":"我只係見到有人食完飯同放工 <br />\n畀警察用棍揮同屌老母"},{"pid":"84efd5c4b060b1cfafb8ea2efc101669fad6ea70","tid":1294060,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T17:38:31.000Z","msg":"無恥到擘大眼講大話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}